data.description: Open House, Saturday, December 2nd, 12pm - 3pm.  Welcome to your next chapter of living in style and comfort! This captivating single-story residence, nestled in the desirable Silver Canyon subdivision, offers the perfect blend of modern convenience and timeless design. As you approach this home, the charm of the brick and stone front facade welcomes you with a touch of sophistication. Situated on a corner lot, this property enjoys an extra sense of space and privacy, making it an ideal retreat within the vibrant community.  With just under 1700 square feet of carefully crafted living space, this Centex-built home showcases a thoughtful floor plan that maximizes both functionality and aesthetic appeal. The seamless flow from room to room provides an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertaining. Location is key, and this home is perfectly situated just off Shaenfield outside of 1604, offering easy access to major thoroughfares and the conveniences of city living. The highly sought-after Northside ISD ensures access to top-tier education for residents.  Step inside, and you'll discover a well-appointed kitchen, spacious living areas, and cozy bedrooms, all bathed in natural light. The water softener and refrigerator, both conveying with the property, add an extra layer of convenience, making this home truly move-in ready. Noteworthy, the washer and dryer also convey, providing further ease for your daily living needs. Plus, enjoy the benefit of no city taxes, enhancing the appeal of this remarkable property.  Embrace the indoor-outdoor lifestyle with a charming backyard space, perfect for al fresco dining or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. Whether you're a first-time buyer or looking to downsize without compromising on quality, this home offers the perfect combination of comfort and style. Don't miss your chance to call this Silver Canyon gem home. Schedule your tour today and experience the best of single-story living in a prime location. Your new chapter begins here!
